These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
2 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Pet   | rabbit  | horse |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: potato, mango
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
2. the person eating mango is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Food   | potato | mango |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, western
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| Game   | mah-jongg | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, chestnut
There 2 different types of food: apricot, tomato
1. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes green is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Color   | chestnut | green   |
| Food       | tomato | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dunhill
There are 2 different nationalities: american, australian
1. the australian is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Cigar   | dunhill    | tiparillo    |
| Nationality   | american | australian |

 #################################

 
